sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant SSH as OpenSSH client
    participant Agent as sshenc-agent
    participant Proto as sshenc-agent-proto
    participant Backend as sshenc-se SshencBackend
    participant Store as ~/.sshenc/keys
    participant LibEA as libenclaveapp
    participant HSM as Secure Enclave / TPM / fallback

    User->>SSH: ssh, scp, sftp, git transport
    SSH->>Agent: Connect via IdentityAgent socket or named pipe
    SSH->>Agent: RequestIdentities
    Agent->>Proto: Parse SSH agent frame
    Agent->>Backend: list()
    Backend->>Store: Read .meta and .pub
    Backend-->>Agent: Allowed identities
    Agent-->>SSH: Public key blobs

    SSH->>Agent: SignRequest(key_blob, challenge)
    Agent->>Proto: Parse and validate request
    Agent->>Backend: Match key and prompt policy
    Backend->>LibEA: sign(label, challenge)
    LibEA->>HSM: Platform signing operation
    HSM-->>LibEA: DER ECDSA signature
    LibEA-->>Backend: Signature bytes
    Backend->>Proto: Convert DER to SSH signature format
    Proto-->>Agent: SSH agent SignResponse
    Agent-->>SSH: Signature
    SSH-->>User: Authentication succeeds or fails
